text: Araecerus palmaris male Araecerus is a genus of beetles belonging to the family Anthribidae. ==Species== *A. coffeae (Fabricius, 1801)(now considered a junior synonym of A. fasciculatus) *A. constans Perkins, 1900 *A. cumingi (Jekel, 1855) *A. fasciculatus (De Geer, 1775) *A. levipennis Jordan, 1924 *A. varians Jordan, 1946 *A. vieillardi (Montrouzier, 1860) Araecerus coffeae Catalogue of life == References == Category:Weevil genera
